            <title>[HBASE-5146] Hbase Shell - allow setting config properties</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-5146</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;It should be possible to set config properties of the cluster/table/column family via the shell and not only via API&lt;br/&gt;
