                            <comment id="13182301" author="zhihyu@ebaysf.com" created="Sun, 8 Jan 2012 21:52:26 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Table / column family attribute change is related to &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-4213&quot; title=&quot;Support for fault tolerant, instant schema updates with out master&amp;#39;s intervention (i.e with out enable/disable and bulk assign/unassign) through ZK.&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;HBASE-4213&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;HBASE-4213&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

