                            <comment id="13506981" author="sershe" created="Fri, 30 Nov 2012 00:32:31 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-7236&quot; title=&quot;add per-table/per-cf configuration via metadata&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;HBASE-7236&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;HBASE-7236&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; is similar (except for cluster level config)&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
